{"tid":272192,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"救命！display port 無訊號","createTime":"2017-06-05T15:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T17:25:09.000Z","uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19287a2bf698c827428fc8331915a031015dbb17","tid":272192,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"搞左成日，可以做既我都做晒，底板/display card/gigabytes/nvidia/mon/win 10 既driver都更新晒。<br />\n上網查過有咩方法，都試過！<br />\n係boost set up停左個UEIV同PCI-E legacy（唔知咩黎）/停仲左個電源選項deep sleep/hdmi同display port一齊插⋯⋯⋯咩野都試過都冇用！點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用緊ryzen1600/gigabyte ab350m gaming3板/gigabyte1060oc6gb卡/asus vg248qe mon<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2008cf5a46c1168888368143f4a65f32b8f2454b","tid":272192,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T02:24:43.000Z","msg":"1.清除CMOS.抆電線抆底板電.正確方法可以睇說明書或網上搵<br />\n唔得就用2<br />\n2.CLEAR CMOS.+ 插一條RAM落去A2. RAM唔好超頻咁開機.睇說明書D設定<br />\n<br />\n1.2試過OK就得<br />\n最後冇辦法先更新BIOS (如非必要唔好更新BIOS)"},{"pid":"f16b6e7fddca8c3ff5514867689d312d3dfd16e6","tid":272192,"uid":115295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"BIOS 默認set咗內置顯示為預設？<br />\n<br />\n定係你嗰Mon冇轉signal？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaf7eb484486092fce201a7f7884623079c32bb","tid":272192,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BIOS 默認set咗內置顯示為預設？<br />\n<br />\n定係你嗰Mon冇轉signal？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我hdmi出到，淨係displayport出唔到！"},{"pid":"914926a03e73eb82d954f356c1637725c7cc287a","tid":272192,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.清除CMOS.抆電線抆底板電.正確方法可以睇說明書或網上搵<br />\n唔得就用2<br />\n2.CLEAR CMOS.+ 插一條RAM落去A2. RAM唔好超頻咁開機.睇說明書D設定<br />\n<br />\n1.2試過OK就得<br />\n最後冇辦法先更新BIOS (如非必要唔好更新BIOS)</blockquote><br />\n1同2都試左喇，都唔得！更新BIOS係咪一定要下載落usb再安裝，官網係咁寫！但係gigabyte 有好似window咁出更新提示，我裝完果個都係咁，唔知係咪一定要入bios裝？<br />\n我今日連線都換埋，應該唔關條線事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626c330ee7a9d95efca0db17f1a66fde633f7793","tid":272192,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"換過條線啦"},{"pid":"3c5195930e42da95b50201036ae71e63b89b3103","tid":272192,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1.清除CMOS.抆電線抆底板電.正確方法可以睇說明書或網上搵<br />\n唔得就用2<br />\n2.CLEAR CMOS.+ 插一條RAM落去A2. RAM唔好超頻咁開機.睇說明書D設定<br />\n<br />\n1.2試過OK就得<br />\n最後冇辦法先更新BIOS (如非必要唔好更新BIOS)</blockquote><br />\n1同2都試左喇，都唔得！更新BIOS係咪一定要下載落usb再安裝，官網係咁寫！但係gigabyte 有好似window咁出更新提示，我裝完果個都係咁，唔知係咪一定要入bios裝？<br />\n我今日連線都換埋，應該唔關條線事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留意Down落USB果個Ver如果同你現有Bios Ver係一樣數字就唔洗喇<br />\n可能壞dp"},{"pid":"74e103492a6f99f2811473d3ae2be10e3c5a3068","tid":272192,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"我今日買左個hdmi轉dislay port，一邊插ps4一邊插個mon，一樣無訊號，我諗係個mon問題！<br />\n我個mon係asus VG248QE，我買左成年唔知有冇保養，我試下問下asus客戶服務！"},{"pid":"aed7b85ce2faf77496c2125086280fcbeda6b187","tid":272192,"uid":90712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"樓主最尾點？"},{"pid":"a19bb34d8592e6e95b7d677f88a4c17b5ec01450","tid":272192,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aed7b85ce2faf77496c2125086280fcbeda6b187","tid":272192,"uid":90712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"樓主最尾點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"ps4插hdmi<br />\n電腦插dvi<br />\n放棄隻mon個display port"}]}